name: Typewriter Pull-Up
instructions: Begin with a standard pull-up by gripping the bar slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.
Pull yourself up until your chin is above the bar.
Shift your body weight to the left, extending your right arm while keeping your left arm bent.
Shift smoothly to the right side, bending your right arm and extending the left arm.
Move back to center, then lower yourself under control to complete one repetition.
